title: Soul Discharge
text:
Soul Discharge () is a 1989 album by <a href="rock%20music">rock</a> band <a href="Boredoms">Boredoms</a>. It was named the 89th greatest album of the 1980s by <a href="Pitchfork%20%28website%29">Pitchfork</a> on the site's initial list of the best albums of the decade.
Track listing.
"Soul Discharge/Early Boredoms".
Despite being a CD release, the songs are divided into only two tracks.
